1. Purpose

The Halisako Cinematic Engine (HCE) is responsible for transforming structured event representations generated by the Halisako Orchestration Engine into cinematic experiences.

The Orchestration Engine determines:

"What happened?"

The Cinematic Engine determines:

"How should the event be experienced?"

The Cinematic Engine converts analytical events into:

character actions
combat choreography
camera direction
emotional tone
environmental reactions
visual effects
pacing
narrative progression

The first implementation targets Chess2Fight, where chess gameplay is transformed into a cinematic battle between opposing armies.

