15. Success Criteria

HCD-301 is considered implemented when:

✅ HXT events can be consumed
✅ Every chess event maps to a cinematic action
✅ HCE JSON schema is generated
✅ Renderer can consume HCE output
✅ Same chess game can generate multiple cinematic interpretations

